  "description": "**Milestone:** Phase 2: Component Expansion\n\nBuild hx-accordion: collapsible content sections for FAQ, expandable content. Progressive enhancement with <details>/<summary> fallback. Single and multi-expand modes.\n\n**Files to Modify:**\n- packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-accordion/\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] Single and multi-expand modes\n- [ ] Animated open/close transitions\n- [ ] Progressive enhancement fallback\n- [ ] Keyboard: Enter/Space to toggle\n- [ ] CSS parts: item, trigger, content, icon\n- [ ] Events: hx-expand, hx-collapse\n- [ ] ARIA: expanded/hidden states\n- [ ] <5KB gzipped\n\n**Complexity:** medium",
